------------
Installation
------------

To reproduce the bug, do the following :

It's just one file :

download mc15_13TeV.361060.Sherpa_CT10_SinglePhotonPt4000_CVetoBVeto.merge.DAOD_TRUTH1.e3587_p2375

cd yourworkdir
setupATLAS
asetup AthAnalysisBase,2.3.22,here

git clone https://github.com/rsmith54/RestFramesCMT.git RestFrames
cd RestFrames
git checkout feature/compileInCmt
cd cmt
cmt config
cmt make

cd yourworkdir
git clone https://github.com/rsmith54/PhotonTruthStudy
cd PhotonTruthStudy/cmt
git checkout feature/segfault
cmt config
cmt make
cd ../share

edit StudyAllPhotonSherpa211_segfault.py
Just change filelist to point to your local version of the file in the DS

athena StudyAllPhotonSherpa211_segfault.py